    "attributes": {
        "action": "Make all term dates across all schools in England the same",
        "additional_details": "I want the Government to make the term dates across all schools in England the same because if you want to go on holiday and you\u2019re kids are at different schools the term dates can be different, which can make it difficult to find dates when both children have school holidays. This can mean parents face fines for taking a child out of school during term time.",
        "background": "I want the Government to make it so all primary and secondary schools in England have the exact same term dates.",
